Interface ConfigStoreValueInspector

    • Method Detail

      • getOwnConfig

        Config getOwnConfig(ConfigKeyPath configKey)
        Obtains the configuration properties directly associated with a given config keys. These will not include any properties/values which can be obtained from the ancestors or imported config keys.
        Parameters:
        configKey - the config key path whose properties are needed.
        Returns:
        the directly specified configuration in Config format for input configKey

      • getResolvedConfig

        Config getResolvedConfig(ConfigKeyPath configKey)
        Obtains a Config object with all implicit and explicit imports resolved, i.e. specified using the Config.withFallback(com.typesafe.config.ConfigMergeable) API.
        Parameters:
        configKey - the path of the configuration key to be resolved
        Returns:
        the Config object associated with the specified config key with all direct and indirect imports resolved.
